    <section id="content" role="main" class="rtp-content-section large-8 medium-6 small-12 columns rtp-multiple-post" >
        
            <h1 class="post-title rtp-main-title">Tags: <span>Big Brother</span></h1>
        <article id="post-15418" class="post-15418 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-news-items tag-big-brother tag-edward-snowden tag-gchq tag-glenn-greenwald tag-jtrig tag-nsa tag-the-intercept clearfix rtp-post-box">
            
            <header class="post-header ">
                
                                            <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/07/16/how-british-spies-seed-the-internet-with-false-info-control-youtube-pageviews-and-manipulate-online-polls/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to How British Spies &#8220;Seed the Internet with False Info, Control YouTube Pageviews and Manipulate Online Polls&#8221;">How British Spies &#8220;Seed the Internet with False Info, Control YouTube Pageviews and Manipulate Online Polls&#8221;</a></h2>
                <?php// rtp_hook_end_post_title(); ?>

                
            <div class="clearfix post-meta post-meta-top"><span class="author"><a class="fn" href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/author/mkriegs/" title="Posts by Michael Krieger">Michael Krieger</a></span> <span class="rtp-meta-separator">|</span> Posted <time class="published" datetime="2014-07-16T14:51:44+00:00">Wednesday Jul 16, 2014</time> at 2:51 pm         <span class="rtp-post-comment-count"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/07/16/how-british-spies-seed-the-internet-with-false-info-control-youtube-pageviews-and-manipulate-online-polls/#comments" class="rtp-post-comment rtp-common-link"  title="Comment on How British Spies &#8220;Seed the Internet with False Info, Control YouTube Pageviews and Manipulate Online Polls&#8221;"><span>14</span> Comments</a></span>
            </div><!-- .post-meta -->            </header><!-- .post-title -->

            <div class="post-content">
                                

                
                <p><img class="alignleft  wp-image-15425" src="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Screen-Shot-2014-07-16-at-2.25.47-PM-300x224.jpg" alt="Screen Shot 2014-07-16 at 2.25.47 PM" width="150" height="112" />Thanks to Edward Snowden, we now have proof about an incredible set of tools used by the British equivalent of the NSA, known as the GCHQ, or Government Communications Headquarters. These tools will essentially confirm every single conspiracy theory you could have ever imagined when it comes to propaganda on the Internet. It allows British intelligence officers to: <strong><em>&#8220;manipulate the results of online polls, artificially inflate pageview counts on web sites, &#8216;amplify&#8217; sanctioned messages on YouTube, and censor video content judged to be &#8216;extremist.&#8217;&#8221;</em></strong></p>
<p>Being the creative folks that they are, GCHQ even came up with code words to describe each &#8220;product.&#8221; These include, UNDERPASS (for poll manipulation), SILVERLORD (for censorship), GESTATOR (for the manipulation of YouTube views), PREDATORS FACE (for DDOS attacks), the list goes on&#8230;</p>
<p> <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/07/16/how-british-spies-seed-the-internet-with-false-info-control-youtube-pageviews-and-manipulate-online-polls/#more-15418" class="more-link">Read the Full Article »</a></p>
<div style=display:inline-block;>
<div style=float:left;margin-right:6px;>
