        <article id="post-9057" class="post-9057 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized tag-american-fascism tag-big-brother tag-nsa tag-patriots tag-snowden tag-you-know-you-are-a-conspiracy-theorist-if clearfix rtp-post-box">
            
            <header class="post-header ">
                
                                            <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2013/11/04/the-definitive-chart-on-how-to-identify-a-terrorist/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to The Definitive Chart on How to Identify a Terrorist">The Definitive Chart on How to Identify a Terrorist</a></h2>
                <?php// rtp_hook_end_post_title(); ?>

                
            <div class="clearfix post-meta post-meta-top"><span class="author"><a class="fn" href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/author/mkriegs/" title="Posts by Michael Krieger">Michael Krieger</a></span> <span class="rtp-meta-separator">|</span> Posted <time class="published" datetime="2013-11-04T20:18:41+00:00">Monday Nov 4, 2013</time> at 8:18 pm         <span class="rtp-post-comment-count"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2013/11/04/the-definitive-chart-on-how-to-identify-a-terrorist/#comments" class="rtp-post-comment rtp-common-link"  title="Comment on The Definitive Chart on How to Identify a Terrorist"><span>3</span> Comments</a></span>
            </div><!-- .post-meta -->            </header><!-- .post-title -->

            <div class="post-content">
                                

                
                <p>A little over a year ago, I wrote an article titled:  <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2012/09/22/you-know-you-are-a-conspiracy-theorist-if/">You Know You Are a Conspiracy Theorist If…</a></p>
<p>It proved a useful description of the varied afflictions that might overcome your fellow man on the path toward becoming a sentient human being. These include critical thinking, the enjoyment of nature and the distrust of mainstream media.</p>
<p>Well now we have the <strong>United States Government Terrorist Identification Chart. </strong>This should further aid you in identifying if there are enemies in your midst. Pay close attention serfs.</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9058" alt="Terrorist chart" src="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Terrorist-chart.jpg" width="640" height="960" /></p>
<p>Great job to whoever created this.</p>
<p>In Liberty,<br />
Mike</p>
<p>Follow me <a href="https://twitter.com/LibertyBlitz">on Twitter!</a></p>
